---
const steps = [
  ['Discover', 'Understand the problem, constraints, budget, users, and what success looks like.'],
  ['Design', 'Create a simple plan that solves the issue without adding unnecessary complexity.'],
  ['Deploy', 'Implement carefully, communicate clearly, and minimize disruption.'],
  ['Document', 'Leave behind the information needed to support, improve, and scale the solution.']
];
---

<section class="section process" id="process">
  <div class="section-head">
    <p class="eyebrow">The approach</p>
    <h2>Built like a partner, not a ticket queue.</h2>
    <p>
      StrataWorks focuses on reliable outcomes: clear scope, clean implementation, security-minded decisions,
      and technology that helps the business instead of becoming another problem to manage.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="timeline">
    {steps.map(([title, text]) => (
      <article>
        <span></span>
        <h3>{title}</h3>
        <p>{text}</p>
      </article>
    ))}
  </div>
</section>